=== workflow for annotation of texts in spreadsheet ===

{{{
select document
generate ID for document (e.g. [abbreviated] title)
register ID in spreadsheet
identify sentences in document
generate IDs for sentences (e.g. running numbers)
for every sentence:
  identify all relevant categories
  for every category thus identified:
    add line to spreadsheet
    add category
    mark document ID in spreadsheet
    mark sentence ID in spreadsheet
    mark word ID in spreadsheet if locus of category is below sentence level
    mark morpheme ID in spreadsheet if locus of category is below word level
    mark discontinuous loci if applicable
}}}

=== workflow for annotation of texts with ELAN ===

=== workflow for annotation of texts with Typecraft ===
http://www.typecraft.org
